stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Monitoring: System Started
    
    Monitoring --> DetectionTriggered: Activity Detected
    DetectionTriggered --> ConfidenceCheck: Process Detection
    
    ConfidenceCheck --> Monitoring: Below Threshold
    ConfidenceCheck --> AudioCheck: Above Threshold
    
    AudioCheck --> AudioFusion: Audio Available
    AudioCheck --> SeverityDetermination: No Audio
    
    AudioFusion --> SeverityDetermination: Fusion Complete
    
    SeverityDetermination --> LowSeverity: Confidence < 0.75
    SeverityDetermination --> MediumSeverity: 0.75 ≤ Confidence < 0.90
    SeverityDetermination --> HighSeverity: Confidence ≥ 0.90
    
    LowSeverity --> EvidenceGeneration: Log to Dashboard
    MediumSeverity --> EvidenceGeneration: Send Email
    HighSeverity --> EvidenceGeneration: Send WhatsApp + Email
    
    EvidenceGeneration --> AlertPending: Clip Generated
    
    AlertPending --> AlertSent: Notifications Delivered
    AlertSent --> AwaitingAcknowledgment: Alert Active
    
    AwaitingAcknowledgment --> Acknowledged: Officer Confirms
    AwaitingAcknowledgment --> Dismissed: False Positive
    AwaitingAcknowledgment --> Escalated: Require Action
    
    Acknowledged --> UnderInvestigation: Case Opened
    Dismissed --> Archived: No Action Needed
    Escalated --> UnderInvestigation: Priority Response
    
    UnderInvestigation --> Resolved: Incident Handled
    UnderInvestigation --> EvidenceRequested: More Info Needed
    
    EvidenceRequested --> UnderInvestigation: Additional Clips Provided
    
    Resolved --> Archived: Close Case
    
    Archived --> [*]: Retention Period Expired
    
    note right of Monitoring
        System continuously
        processes video streams
    end note
    
    note right of ConfidenceCheck
        Threshold: 0.65
        Filters noise
    end note
    
    note right of HighSeverity
        Immediate response
        Multi-channel alert
    end note
    
    note right of AwaitingAcknowledgment
        Timeout: 30 minutes
        Auto-escalate if no response
    end note
    
    note right of Archived
        Default retention: 90 days
        Configurable per policy
    end note